  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add onion, garlic, and ginger, and cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add ground clove and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add red lentils, confit-tomato, and salt, and stir to combine.",
    "Add 2 cups of water and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes, or until the lentils are tender.",
    "Use an immersion blender to puree the curry until smooth.",
    "Taste and adjust seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve the curry in scallop shells, garnished with fresh herbs."
